    given-names: Helbert
    alias: HelbertMoura
repository-code: "https://github.com/HelbertMoura/ai_launcher"
url: "https://github.com/HelbertMoura/ai_launcher"
abstract: >-
  Desktop launcher Windows (Tauri v2 + React 18 + Rust) pra gerenciar,
  instalar e executar CLIs de IA (Claude Code, Codex, Gemini, Qwen e
  outros). A v5.0+ adiciona suporte opt-in a providers Anthropic-
  compatible alternativos (Z.AI/GLM, MiniMax) com mapeamento automático
  de modelos.
keywords:
  - tauri
  - windows
  - ai
  - cli
  - claude-code
  - launcher
  - devtools
